title: JAN 31 2022 - OTTAWA POLICE ATTEMPT TO BREAK UP MASSIVE TRUCKER PROTEST IN CANADA
description:
The Ottawa police attempt to break up a massive trucker protest in Canada and downtown workers have been asked to work from home due to the protest, new analytics reveal that the Bill Kristol group spent nearly $40 million on behalf of the left, Sen. Graham backs Pres. Biden’s pledge to pick a black woman, saying it will “make the court look more like America”, and billionaire mega donor Soros pledges an ‘unprecedented’ $125 million to leftist political allies in 2022. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
